headline: Strength Seen in FuelCell Energy (FCEL): Can Its 7.5% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: FuelCell Energy (FCEL) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
